  "textPreview": "Free June 9 event: How to win brand visibility when AI decides what gets seen →\nSolutions\nTools\nResources\nPricing\nEN\nSign in\nRequest a demo\nStart free trial\nChatGPT Visibility Tracker\n\nGet the full picture of your brand in ChatGPT answers. Monitor mentions, review competitors, and optimize your AI presence with one of the most reliable ChatGPT visibility tracking software available\n\nStart free trial\nRequest a demo\n\nNo credit card required\n\nTrusted by 40,000+ agencies\n\nChatGPT Visibility Tracker\n\nTrack brand and website visibility within ChatGPT\n\nCheck how ChatGPT answers your target queries\n\nDetect and track ChatGPT brand mentions and links\n\nSee where your brand ranks in ChatGPT answers\n\nMonitor how often your competitors are featured\n\nMeasure ChatGPT visibility trends with historical data\n\nStart free trial\nPut ChatGPT visibility data to work across your stack\n\nAccess SEO and GEO data via API or query it live inside your AI assistants via MCP\n\nYour data where your team needs it\n\nPull brand mentions, link data, and competitor ChatGPT visibility metrics directly via API into the tools your team already uses.\n\nReporting that reflects your clients’ priorities\n\nConnect SEO & GEO data to Data Studio or AgencyAnalytics and build client dashboards that go beyond standard reports.\n\nWorkflows that run on their own\n\nAutomate marketing processes across all your client projects via Make.com, n8n, or Zapier integrations.\n\nQuery your data inside your AI assistants\n\nAsk Claude, ChatGPT, or other AI systems about your brand's visibility trends directly via MCP and get the data back.\n\nStart free trial\nAnalyze your brand reputation in ChatGPT and beyond! Build a consistent story aligned with your strategy\nTry now\nA ChatGPT visibility optimization tool that covers all your needs\n\nUse our top-notch tool to track brand visibility in ChatGPT and eliminate blind spots in your AI search strategy\n\nUnderstand how ChatGPT describes your brand\n\nSee what ChatGPT says about your business and how ",
